view.menu

Class MenuFrameImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.menu.MenuFrameImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MenuFrame

    public final class MenuFrameImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements MenuFrame
    The main frame of the menu game. It contains all the panels that can be shown in a CardLayout. It defines also the starting page and the background music.
